ttf-open-sans (True Type font)

Open Sans is a clean and modern sans-serif typeface designed by Steve
Matteson and commissioned by Google. It is especially designed for
legibility across print, web, and mobile interfaces.

Open Sans is excellent for any type of use. It's incredibly readable
in small sizes and also works great when printed in huge letters.
The best thing of all, it's a free font! You are free to use and
download it for your next design project.

It's a well known and modern font that is being used more and more
on new websites. Because of its simplicity it really makes your
content easily readable. The same thing goes for offline content.
When printed it will make your documents amazing.
